# Strategy analysis — voice profile (template)

This file is the **canonical compiled voice profile** the backend injects into
every LLM prompt. Treat it as the distilled output of all your other working
files (boundaries.md, tone.md, writing_patterns.md, etc.). Keep it
single-source: the LLM sees this, not the fragments.

Copy this file to `voice_profile/strategy_analysis.md` and replace the
placeholder text below with your own distillation. The backend will refuse
to start until the runtime file exists.

---

